name: FastXCel
body:
## FastXCel
C# component for creating/editing Excel'2007-2013 (.xlsx) files without running any other software and libraries
#### Fist pre-release (ver. 0.1)
Binary for win32 (.Net Framework ver 4.5): [get it here!](https://github.com/devgopher/fastxcel/releases/tag/0.1)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
